                     <interp inst="t18400914-2375-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>stealing, on the <rs id="t18400914-cd-133" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400914-2375-offence-1 t18400914-cd-133"></join>1st of September</rs>, 1 ewe, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18400914-name-781" type="victimName">
