                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400914-2375-offence-1 t18400914-name-781"></join>George Johnson</persName>.—2nd <hi rend="smallCaps">COUNT</hi>, for killing the ewe, with intent to steal the carcase;</rs> to which <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAM BIGGS</hi> pleaded</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18400914-2375-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18400914-2375-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
